{"tid":1394104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE走紅毯⋯Momo突然慘叫！7妞嚇成一團 多賢衝出救成員","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T19:45:27.000Z","uid":74065,"like":19,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4442411b2604be0cf6dfc2fe0224acfce6afe05c","tid":1394104,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:00:07.000Z","msg":"南韓人氣女團TWICE於1日出席MGMA第一屆頒獎典禮，成員Mina雖淚灑機場引起各界關注，但其餘8位成員敬業地撐起笑容，穿著復古風格的禮服亮麗現身，面對鏡頭微笑打招呼。就在她們接受訪問時，一隻蟲子卻誤闖台上，Momo嚇到花容失色，成員在直播中爆出淒慘尖叫聲，所幸多賢衝出去打蟲，解決插曲。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE於1日出席MGMA第一屆頒獎典禮，8位成員有人綁著俏麗辮子、有人梳起馬尾、有人以氣質波浪捲現身，搭配清新風格的復古裝配，一出場就秒殺攝影大哥的底片。然而，她們在接受訪問時，一隻蟲子突然出現在舞台上，MoMo嚇壞爆出大尖叫緊抱著成員，7人在直播前嚇成一團，膽子大的多賢立刻衝出去幫忙趕走蟲，志效則是幽默表示：「在等待的時候，連蟲子都還歡迎我們。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4276/d4276854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4276%2Fd4276854.jpg&h=1cd4c80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多賢❤❤❤❤❤❤❤"},{"pid":"4e62f1744341464ff1ddf1b929e27eb3abb0ca95","tid":1394104,"uid":138138,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"好變態囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又殺生。。。"},{"pid":"e0e0af9b82418a99e7be7a70352677c634f556a4","tid":1394104,"uid":74065,"like":35,"dislike":12,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"4e62f1744341464ff1ddf1b929e27eb3abb0ca95","tid":1394104,"uid":138138,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"好變態囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又殺生。。。"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"殺生個個唔係到"},{"pid":"c28d466c063138740056ef2343a04ff5f72cbd0c","tid":1394104,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0e0af9b82418a99e7be7a70352677c634f556a4","tid":1394104,"uid":74065,"like":35,"dislike":12,"score":23,"quote":{"